===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|dey·∏±}}
Borrowed from {{bor|en|ML.|dictionarium}}, from {{der|en|la|dictionarius}}, from {{m|la|dictio||speaking}}, from {{m|la|dictus}}, perfect past participle of {{m|la|dƒ´c≈ç||speak}} + {{m|la|-arium||room, place}}.

