===Etymology 2===
* {{sense|highest rank|grade|music}} From the initial position of the letter {{m|en|A}} in the English alphabet.
* {{sense|blood type}} From {{m|en|w:ABO blood group system|A antigen}}
* {{sense|vehicle-distinguishing signs}} From {{m|en|Austria}}

====Symbol====
{{rfc|en}}
{{en-symbol}}

# The highest rank on any of various scales that assign letters.
#: {{ux|en|We assign each item inspected a rating from '''A''' through G, depending on various factors. &mdash; An A-rated bond.}}
# {{lb|en|education}} The highest [[letter grade]] assigned (disregarding plusses and minuses).
#: {{ux|en|I was so happy to get an '''A''' on that test.}}
# {{lb|en|music}} A tone three fifths above C in the [[cycle of fifths]]; the sixth tone of the C major scale; the first note of the minor scale of A minor; the reference tone that occurs at exactly 440 Hz; the printed or written note A; the [[scale]] with A as its [[keynote]].<ref name=SOED/><ref name=OCD>{{R:OCD2|page=1}}</ref>
#: {{ux|en|Orchestras traditionally tune to a concert '''A'''.}}
# {{lb|en|medicine}} A [[blood type]] that has a specific antigen that aggravates the immune response in people with type [[B]] antigen in their blood. They may receive blood from type A or type [[O]] but cannot receive blood from [[AB]] or [[B]].
#: {{ux|en|My blood type is '''A''' negative.}}
# {{lb|en|chemistry}} [[mass number|Mass number]].
# {{lb|en|logic}} A universal affirmative suggestion.<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=1}}</ref>
# Acoustic source.
# Actual weight of an aircraft.
# {{lb|en|historical}} {{abbreviation of|[[adulterer]], [[adulteress]]|lang=en}}.
# {{w|Alaska Steamship Company}}.
# {{w|Alcoa Steamship Company}}.
# [[allele|Allele]] dominant.
# {{w|Alveolar gas equestion|Alveolar gas}}.
# {{w|American Stock Exchange}}.
# Ammunition examiner.
# {{w|Anchor Line}}.
# [[aspect ratio|Aspect ratio]].
# {{w|Assembly Bill}}.
# Smallest of the [[brassiere]] cup sizes.
# Chemical activity.
# First [[van der Waals constant]].
# [[Fraunhofer line]] for [[oxygen]].
# {{lb|en|aviation}} [[hail|Hail]].
# {{lb|en|in newspaper stock listings}} Includes extras.
# Linear [[acceleration]].
# Mean sound absorption coefficient.
# Shoe size narrower than B.
# {{lb|en|baseball}} Single A league, one of the lowest professional leagues.
# Total acidity.

