<references/>

In order to allow [[Module:syllables]] to count syllables, the disyllabic sequence {{IPAchar|/i…ô/}} must be transcribed with a period to mark the syllable break &ndash; {{IPAchar|/i.…ô/}} &ndash; so that it will not be confused with the New Zealand diphthong {{IPAchar|/i…ô/}}.

{{IPAchar|/…π/}} in the vowel plus {{IPAchar|/…π/}} sequences is sometimes replaced with {{IPAchar|/…ö/}}: {{IPAchar|/√∞…õ…ö/}} instead of {{IPAchar|/√∞…õ…π/}}. In order to keep [[Module:syllables]] from counting {{IPAchar|/…ö/}} as a syllable, add the non-syllabic diacritic: {{IPAchar|/√∞…õ…öÃØ/}}.

