==English==

===Etymology 1===
[[Image:The Raven.jpg|thumb|right|A raven (bird).]]
From {{inh|en|enm|raven}}, {{m|enm|reven}}, from {{inh|en|ang|hr√¶fn}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*hrabnaz}} (compare {{cog|is|hrafn}}, {{cog|nl|raaf}}, {{cog|de|Rabe}}, {{cog|da|-}} and {{cog|nb|ravn}}, {{cog|nn|ramn}}), from {{der|en|ine-pro|*·∏±orh‚ÇÇ-}}. Compare {{cog|mga|cr√∫}}, {{cog|la|corvus}}, {{cog|lt|≈°√°rka||magpie}}, {{cog|sh|svr»Åka}} ‚Äòid.‚Äô, {{cog|grc|Œ∫œåœÅŒ±Œæ}}), from {{m|ine-pro|*·∏±er-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*·∏±or-}}. Compare furthermore {{cog|la|crep≈ç||I creak, crack}}, {{cog|sa|‡§ï‡•É‡§™‡§§‡•á||he laments, he implores}}.

